# /b-advisor

Run the AI Bridge advisor for the user's task and use the resulting decision as handoff context.

If the user writes `/b-advisor <task>`, run:

```powershell
.\b-advisor "<task>"
```

If the user writes `/b-advisor review`, run:

```powershell
.\b-advisor review
```

If the user writes `/b-advisor triage <task>`, run:

```powershell
.\b-advisor triage "<task>"
```

After the command finishes, read the printed run directory and summarize `.ai-bridge/runs/<timestamp>/decision.md`.
